<!-- ========== FAQ ========== -->
<section id="faq" class="lr-section lr-section-bordered lr-fade-in">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lr-section-header lr-section-header-center">
      <h2 class="lr-section-heading">Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <p class="lr-section-desc">Everything you need to know about working with us</p>
    </div>
    <div class="lr-faq-list lr-stagger">
      <div class="lr-faq-item lr-stagger-item">
        <button class="lr-faq-question">
          What kind of AI projects do you build?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lr-faq-answer">
          <p>We build custom AI agents, LLM-powered applications, RAG systems, intelligent automation pipelines, and full-stack products with AI at the core. If it involves AI and software, we can build it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-faq-item lr-stagger-item">
        <button class="lr-faq-question">
          What technologies and AI models do you work with?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lr-faq-answer">
          <p>We work with OpenAI, Anthropic Claude, open-source models like Llama and Mistral, plus frameworks like LangChain, Rails, React, and Python. We pick the best tools for your specific use case.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-faq-item lr-stagger-item">
        <button class="lr-faq-question">
          How long does a typical project take?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lr-faq-answer">
          <p>Discovery sprints take 2 weeks. Full product builds typically range from 6-16 weeks depending on scope. We move fast with AI-assisted development and ship iteratively so you see progress early.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-faq-item lr-stagger-item">
        <button class="lr-faq-question">
          Do you work with startups or only enterprises?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lr-faq-answer">
          <p>Both. We've helped early-stage startups build their first AI-powered MVP and partnered with established companies to integrate AI into existing products. Our engagement models adapt to your stage and budget.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-faq-item lr-stagger-item">
        <button class="lr-faq-question">
          Will we own the code and IP?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lr-faq-answer">
          <p>Yes, 100%. Everything we build for you is yours. Full source code, documentation, and deployment assets are transferred to you. No lock-in, no hidden dependencies.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-faq-item lr-stagger-item">
        <button class="lr-faq-question">
          How do we get started?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lr-faq-answer">
          <p>Reach out through our contact page. We'll schedule a free discovery call to understand your goals, then propose the right engagement model and timeline. No commitment required to start the conversation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

